Anne Aubrey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anne_Aubrey 0 Anne Aubrey (born 1 January 1937) is a retired English film actress. She was mainly active in Warwick Films in the 1950s and 1960s. She worked with Anthony Newley in such films as Idle on Parade, Killers of Kilimanjaro, The Bandit of Zhobe (1959), Jazz Boat, Let's Get Married, and In the Nick (1960). She also appeared in the 1961 western The Hellions, opposite Richard Todd. Anne_Aubrey ( born 1_January_1937 ) is a_retired_English_film_actress .
